description:
HellYeah - Thank You (Single/EP) 2007-2015 

Hellyeah is an American heavy metal supergroup, consisting of Mudvayne lead vocalist Chad Gray, Nothingface guitarist Tom Maxwell, bass player Kyle Sanders, Rhythm Guitarist Christian Brady and former Pantera and Damageplan drummer Vinnie Paul.

"Thank You" is the third single by heavy metal band Hellyeah from their debut album Hellyeah. The song is a tribute to all of the band's recently departed family members: Vinnie Paul's brother Dimebag Darrell, Tom Maxwell's mother, and Chad Gray's grandmother. The song reached #37 on the Billboard Hot Rock Tracks chart.

Later an opportunity arose and  this Single/EP was created and uploaded to a Selection of file sharing sites. 

It is unknown how much exposure this release achieved due to the fact
that this description was published simultaneously with the release.
